title.narrative: PROCOFSERVICES and P0287 for SAF Governance Programme for Helmand

description.narrative: This activity (PROCOFSERVICES and P0287 for SAF Governance Programme for Helmand) is a component of Helmand Governance reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £104,541. This component benefits Afghanistan, and works in the following sector(s): Decentralisation and support to subnational government, Civilian peace-building, conflict prevention and resolution. The start date is 01-05-2008 and the end date is 31-03-2012.
